%h2
  Already subscribed!

%p
  Your email
  %code
    = recipient.email
  is already in the list
  = succeed '.' do
    = "##{list.id}"

- if redirect
  %p
    Click
    %a{href: redirect} here
    to get back to where you came from.

%p
  If you want to unsubscribe,
  = succeed '.' do
    %a{href: '/unsubscribe?token=' + CGI.escape(token)} click here

